latestPosts.caption:
Yoga isn’t just a practice, it’s a way of being.
My favourite asanas are:

🧘‍♀️ Sukhasana with Chin Mudra – It helps me centre myself, calms the chaos within, and connects me with my breath. In this simple seated pose, I find peace even on the noisiest days.

🙏 Sukhasana with Anjali Mudra – A moment of gratitude. Folding my hands at the heart reminds me to pause, appreciate, and stay grounded no matter what life throws at me.

These poses may look simple, but their stillness holds the power to transform. 🌿

latestPosts.caption:
Coming Home
I wandered far with restless feet,
Chased distant suns and foreign streets.
Yet in my soul, a whisper stirred—
A lullaby I always heard.

Not made of gold, nor carved in stone,
But love-worn walls I called my own.
The scent of chai, the creak of doors,
The echoing laugh on polished floors.

A mother’s sari, soft and bright,
The flicker of the porch's light.
A father's silence, deep and kind,
The gentle peace I left behind.

And when I stood at threshold's grace,
With tears that time could not erase—
I knew the truth I longed to roam:
The heart will always lead you home
@notion.press
